    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below MRL 5 requirements, the regulatory submission proceeds under a risk-based justification that the Monte Carlo UQ bounds are conservative and the primary validation result narrative provides sufficient experimental detail to support the hemolysis prediction claim. The structured provenance of the primary validation activity was not formally registered in the evidence package; the assessment team determined the prose narrative in the ValidationResult description to be an adequate substitute for the Activity link. This decision is accepted pending FDA review.",
